YAYAYA

Its a snowday today!

I think...

well it's 5:30 and i can't sleep so i went on the computer until i know that there is a snow day...which im pretty sure there is.

Wow im extremely tired!

My so called life is on.

I usually watch it anyway at this time while i wait for my hair to air dry.

Wow i need a life!

Well atleast im not doing some dumb ballet workout at 4 in the morning...like others.......

ahh i think im getting sick

Staller center rehersaks are  wednesday thursday and friday! Its crasy! Everything came so fast this year.

People may come to see me but i don't really want them to because ill be slightly embarassed.

arfff

im tired!

wow i have a new and huge obsession with niel young and bob dylan!

both are extremely amazing!

so i decided that i have the uggliest livejournal ever. so i majorly need to make it better in like 2 minutes.


this weekend was so wierd. 

friday- i was supposed to be in a haunted house with my friend jakie but ballet rehersals ruins peoples lives. Then i was supposed to go to ari's but  satan i mean my mom grounded me for "challenging" her or so she calls it. Then i was invited to go to annas house with sneha and i was able to go. Only because it would make the driving situation to dance easier on my mother.

At annas house we at hot pockets and made smores and then we gave her dog a walk. Apparently anna walks her dog every night really late for like mile and a half. While we were walking  i decided that the stars were really pretty so i impulsively started lying on the road in the middle of the street and then her dog came over and stepped on my mouth. But the stars are amazing in greenport and coram is shafted and has like no night sky.


When we got home from our walk we went into her room and anna and sneha broke her couch/bed. Then i fell asleep and woke up to celine dion ave maria blasting. I was so confused. 

The next morning we woke up and got tea at this tea place. We got the tea for two special complete with scones and sandwiches and desserts. We got cinamon and choaclate mint tea. The cinnamon was incredible but the chocolate tasted like ass. 

We left for dance and then took class. Which was such a waste of time because dimitri decides tp make us wait 23890 hours for his decision to cancel rehersals. We didnt even have to go.. AHHH

When i got home i fell asleep form like 5-9:00

i feel gross but im not showering. 

wow i need a haircut

seeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee yyyyyyyyyaaaaaaaaaaa

wow i haven't written in a long time.

I think i'll start to write regurally again.

Well today was a shitty day.

 Im at ballet in the library and children are due at any moment to come in this room and ask me questions in which the answer is obvious. Such as "Is that a Laptop!!?!!"  "YOUR ON THE INTERNET AT BALLET" and stuff like that. 

So nutcracker shit has started once again. For those who know what it was like last year, it is worse this year.

Dimitris being retarted and pissing EVERYONE off. 

I am a girl at the party this year. Like what the hell. I was a boy for 3 years and now they put me as a girl. I like being a boy thank you very much. I wonder how wrong this sounds for someone who has no idea what i'm talking about.

Im in a new school this year. Longwood yup. Its a huge school with aprox 3,700 kids. No joke. Thats a huge transition. Also the students are totally different. Everyone wants sex and thats all the guys care about. Well the gangster ones for the most part.


Ha dimitri just walked in and now is talking to himself. 

Yeah its pretty funny.


Okay he is gone

So anyway. Yeah as i was saying. 
School sucks

I guess its not that bad though,

Its better than being home all day long

So i have to go cause i have to pee

eww my coffeee just got rly cold.. gerrrossss

seeeeeee yaaaa

Wow i havent written in so long but i guess ill start now.

I will start of by saying that last week was extreme torture! 
and if i said that BESFI had nothing ot do with my previous statement...i would be lying.

Being that vicki wasn't there i had no one to talk to.

at all.

Since Cherie wasn't there Blair had no on to talk with also.

Every day when i went into the dressing room for lunch (refusing to eat with the group of bitches..--no names needed---) blaire would come along and talk to me.

The first day i didn't care that much but as the days went on i was afraid that while she was rambling about some meaningless shit i would lunge across the room and begin to strangle her. I dont mean to be completely violent or anything.. but she was just really pissing me off. SHE JUST DOESN'T STOP TALKING.

I felt a little bad though because on thursday she was talking about how she wanted choclate but claims she 
can't have any in fear that she will gain weight and then she was rambling how all her friends yell at her and tell her to eat more because she is too skinny. 

My responce was a cold stare that basically said " are you fucking kidding me?"

She was obviously rubbing it in my face and bragging about how skinny she is and shit and pretending that she hates when people say she is too thin although we both know that she loves it. 
So after she realized the look on my face and shut up for the first time in 20 minutes, i left the room.

Thank god i missed monday because four days of blair is engough.

i only missed on monday because i quit ballet....for a day

i was really honest with my mom and told her that i feel like there is nothing in dance for me and that i am wasting my time.

after and hour and a half of explaining she finally said " if this is really what you want to do then it is your decision"

so i didnt go the next day to besfi but then when i heard her say  " if i had the oppurtunities that she has i would never give them up...blah blah blah blah blah"

so that made me feel like crap and for some reason i feel like i can't let my mom down. and that i would be fine with quiting if she was okay with it but i cant stand the thought of her being dissapointed in me. i know it might sound weird but that is that.

okay so thats enough of the dance subject.

i have my own room for one week!! yayayayayayay! 

well only because the music room that was built for my brothers to record in is free because they are recording in LA at the moment but while they where gone for the past 2 months my brother paul used that as his room but now that hewent on vaca in dominican republic it was free and i took it.
and this is the first time i am able to have my own room.
THE FIRST TIME IN MY LIFE!

it is the best thing ever!!!!!!!!

---i saw charlie and the choclate factory. 

being that i love johnny depp and the original movie i loved the second one..althoough it was a little boring in the middle...i still like it alot.
well i have to go now because if i dont my sister will have my head.

buuuuuhhh byeesssss

Well its about 7:00 in the morning and i talked my mom into letting me stay home from school. Well im updating now because i had this dream (with you guys in it) and i knew i would forget so i wanted to post it as soon as i could.

SO this is THE DREAM:


I was on my way to sieskaya and eveything was going normal until i got in there. ALL I could remember was that my hair was all a mess and valia stared yelling at me. Then when i walked into class you guys were there visiting. But all i see is that sarah cut her hair to her chin and died it black and Elizabeth just sitting there giving everyone death looks. So after i say hi to you guys we started class but the lights were off and instead of ussing the barre we were all using the front of cars. Then out of nowhere i am in a health food store and my mom was talking with some guy and i started crying because i couldn't hear anyone. Then i ended up at the dumb besfi competition and then thats all i remembered. 


So that was my dream. And now that i wrote that down...i am going back to bed!

Yesterday was mothers day and we went out for dinner with my dads side of the family. We attempted to have a nice/quiet dinner at a awesome resturant called amici's, but when we got there and realized that they screwed up our reservation ..nice/quiet was not included in our vocabulary. My uncle was being hysterical and almost killed that manager. It was so loud in that room and we were waiting to be seated for over an hour. When we finnaly were seated they stuck the 15 of us in a corner!! First of all i am no  Mary-Kate olsen and they stuck me in a corner that not even and emaciated freak could fit in. But they felt bad for making us wait and giving us the crapiest seats ever that they kept on giving us all this bread and olive oil.


The food was really good but i wasn't feeling well and i didn't want that much to eat but i did have some salad and spinach and pasta. We left the restaurant and came home. I watched about 37042170127401 episodes of i love lucy and happy days and then i fell asleep. So that was my mothers day. Well i have to head off for school. buh bye

WOW! haven't updated in a while. Im so tired. I woke up this morning at 7:00 to go to work at 8:00 where i remained until 5:00. It is insane how much time filing medical records can consume. Im working ot make money so i can go to puerto rico, so im basically spending my whole vacation working. But i really don't care becuase id rather not have a real vacation now ,where all i would be doing is sitting home, as opposed to working and getting money to go to puerto rico. TO me...there is no comparasson. 

So the BESFI show went well yesterday. Although my doubles weren't perfect i had so much fun on stage doing gang . I coulndn't stop laughing while i was on stage because justin (one of my fellow skull gang members) took a pixie stick on stage and was snorting it up his nose as if it were cocaine. It was one of those things where you have to be there to laugh. But at the moment i was dying of lauhgter.

I stayed home from dance today because im tired from work and my stomach hurts. It hurst even worse when i eat and my momma made artichokes tonight. GEEZE LOUISE! Okay well i guess i should get back to watching seinfeld, although i hate the episode thats on. Its the one where they forget where they parked thier car in the mall parking lot. WEll buh bye yall!

So i missed a total of 3 days of school and dance. And its really strange that i want to go back to them both. I thought i would never be saying this (like EVER) but i hate missing school. Not as if i miss my psycotic teachers or anythin of a sort..i just hate missing work and having to catch up on it. This whole thing started on tuesday. Well i went to the doctors office three times this month going back each time because i had this damn cold that just wouldnt go away. So i went back to the doctor for the third time on tuesday. The last other times i went these other doctors were a little ditsy( to say the least) but on tuesday i had my normal one, who my mother and i have come to notice that shes a lesbian (but thats a whole other story). So anyway on tuesday i went to see me doctor and she said that my spleen was slightly enlarged and said that she noticed how shitty i looked and i might have mono. So she gave my mom this paper of the blood work and crap and so i had to get blood work taken from my poor arm..which by the way is still swollen from that damn needle. So when i went on wednesday to get blood taken i was scared out of my mind. And the past experiences that i had when i had previous blood work didnt help at all. So it hurt like hell and they had this song  playing ,while blood was flowing out of my viens and into tubes ,and my mother kept asking me "michelle do you know who plays this song" "michelle..who plays this song" "michelle.. whos the artist who plays this song" ...i mean as if i cared at all. So i didnt get the results to the test back yet and i really cant do anything until i get them back because if i do get mono i am still contagious until treated. so yeyaya..my life for the past four days consisted of lesbian doctors, wathching t.v. ,sleeping, and needles. isnt it great!

Happy Easter! Wow today was an interesting day. 



I woke up at 7:30 to my mothers voice(not a good way to start out a day) and i took a shower and got ready for church. I was planning to wear my skirt that i bought in the city but i forgot to shave my legs. So at the last minute right before going to church i shaved my legs with cream and a mysterious razor i found in my drawer. Now i have this rash from my ankle to my knee. So besides that point..i went to church and on the way there all my parents did was fight. Its like theres this spirit that comes out on the holidays that causes them to fight. I guess they call that stress but honestly, how can you get stressed on easter? Its not like christmas or thanksgiving or anything. 


So after church i came home. We got bagels but i still have no appetite so i didnt have one. Which is insane because i love bagels. Then after that we just hung out at home. I was playing with my nephew who i am so in love with! I can't take it anymore. Well while i was playing with him i noticed his breath was really really really really bad. And it has been like that for a few days now. And its not like morning breath or like just ate garlic and olives breath,...it was like something died and is rotting in my body breath. So we researched online whta could be the cause of this incredibly gross breath and one of the causes was something caught in the nasal passage. So my brother (his dad) looked up his nose and saw something green peekin out. So we assumed it was a pee and he stuck it up there not knowing it would make his breath smell like ass. So we tried to get it out with many ways but then we decided not to take matters into our own hands and bring him to the emergency room. Since its easter there were not many people there. So we got in and out in a matter of 40 minutes which is unbelievable for the ER. It turns out that he stuck a piece of green styrafoam in his nose. Yes.,.it was quite wierd the first time i heard it too. So then we ate dinner and i still wasn't hungry. But i did have some food becuase my mother thought i was crash dieting. Then we watched that show about the "strongest boy in the world" thing. So those were the events that took place on this strange family day.

Haven't updated in a while with an acutal entry and not a survey or a quiz. So i guess nows the time. I can't fall asleep and ive been in bed trying to fall asleep for about two hours. I feel really sick. I haven't eaten all day because i have not apetite and i get nauseous at the sight of food. My chest hurts really bad also. I think im dying.(that wasn't at the least bit dramatic) Sorry to be a bitch and complain but thats what im feeling like right now. Well anyway, on a lighter note, tomorrows easter and im staying home and doing nothing. For once! Normally we make a huge ordeal and have 1723809472109 people over the house, but not this year. This year its just the 11 of us (includin devon..aka the cutest child ever) eating a normal meal (hopefully i can eat by then) at home. Actually its just going to be the 9 of us beacause Josh and Joe are still on tour. I think they are going to be in Oklahoma or something. Okay well im going to put a movie on and try to fall asleep on the couch or something. xoxo

Okay im tired and i think ill pay a visit to that cabinet.
